name: Winter Style SD 2.1
description:
This is an SD 2.1 version of my SD 1.5 Winter Style; a Textual Inversion Style Embedding trained on images of a snowy winter forest/cabin scene. You can get amazing winter colors and snow effects in your images by calling Style-Winter in the positive prompt.

If you need the effect to come through stronger, try doubling up the Style-Winter trigger words, or moving them closer to the front of the prompt.

Please consider joining my Patreon! Advanced SD tutorials, settings explanations, adult-art, from a female content creator (me!) patreon.com/theally
